

.. and did you search cpan for FOO ?


========================
Let Me CPAN That For You
========================

A toy app made in a weekend with Web::Simple and HTML::Zoom.

Examples: 
  http://lmctfy.org/catalyst
  http://lmctfy.org/MooseX::*/m
  http://lmctfy.org/petdance/a
  http://lmctfy.org/bioperl/d

Go try it at http://lmctfy.org!

Inspired on http://lmgtfy.com. In their own words: "This is for all those
people that find it more convenient to bother you with their question rather
than google it for themselves.".
